[p 
	"For example, if you wanted to link to the YouTube video at 
	[em 
		"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mBSE2QkHMeU
	]em
	", you would use [video]http
	[em 
	]em
	"://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mBSE2QkHMeU[/video], and 
	[b 
		"not
	]b
	" [video]mBSE2QkHMeU[/video] or any sort of embed code you find on a particular site.
	$LF
]p
